---
title: Industrially | Blog
---

<div class="bg-white">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-2xl mb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto flex flex-col gap-6 sm:gap-12">
      <h1 class="text-text text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-6xl font-bold">Blog</h1>
      <% site = Sitepress::Site.new %>
      <% posts = site.resources.glob("blog/*html*").select { _1.data.date.to_date <= Date.current }.sort_by { _1.data.date.to_date }.reverse %>
      <% posts.each do |post| %>
        <a href="<%= post.request_path %>" class="p-4 sm:p-6 border bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg flex flex-col gap-2 hover:border-gray-300 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="prose prose-sm sm:prose lg:prose-lg">
            <h3 class="mb-2"><%= post.data[:title] %></h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500"><%= post.data[:description] %></p>
          </div>
        </a>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-gray-50 py-8 sm:py-10 md:py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-text leading-tight">Aprende a usar software para potenciar tu negicio de distribución industrial</h2>
      <p class="mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-xl sm:max-w-2xl mx-auto">Aquí compartimos pequeños tips, consejos y herramientas sobre todo relacionadas al uso de software en negocios de distribución y ventas de equipo industrial.</p>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-full sm:max-w-xl md:max-w-2xl mt-6 sm:mt-8">
        <script async data-uid="5946107901" src="https://bhserna.ck.page/5946107901/index.js"></script>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</div>
